data.description: Welcome to a cozy 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home nestled in East Orlando. As you enter, you are greeted by an open concept living space that seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and ample storage space. Both primary and second bedroom are large in size and feature walk-in closets. Enjoy the outdoor oasis in Florida room that offers a tranquil space to unwind and take in the backyard views offering privacy and year around comfort. Located in a bustling neighborhood with easy access to shopping, dining, entertainment, and Valencia CC. Don't miss the opportunity to make this quaint home your own.
